&lt;p&gt;发送一条消息进行测试，找到 simple.queue 进行发送消息&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PigPigLetsGo/imeages/master/202310221030573.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20231022103002600&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
